                            <comment id="17924908" author="JIRAUSER305181" created="Fri, 7 Feb 2025 14:21:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The main issue is deciding which flag(--standalone, --initial-controllers, or --no-initial-controllers) should be used in run time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is tricky to distinguish which mode we should use; we don&apos;t have further information to judge it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think the most straightforward approach is to only support `&#8211;standalone` in 4.0. Then, we should have a KIP for adding new parameters when running docker wrapper.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
